@node what "What is DawnVideoPoker?"

@{b}What is DawnVideoPoker?@{ub}

It's a Video Poker Machine Simulator, with standard poker @{"rules" link rules}, found
in many bars & casinos. It includes a @{"'Double or Nothing'" link double} subgame that
really makes VideoPoker the game it is.

There are also two features or sub-games; @{"ACES HIGH" link acehi} and @{"STAR GAME" link stargame} which
are not "VideoPoker standard" but inventions of mine that really spices up
the game (and maybe makes the win-% a little too high -- but they can be
turned off ;))

@{b}What's in it?@{ub}

* @{"Double feature" link double} (This is what VideoPoker is About!)
* @{"'ACES HIGH'" link acehi} Bonus feat. Collect all 4 ACES and QUADRUPLE profit. (V2.0)
* @{"'STAR GAME'" link stargame} Bonus feat. Earn 3 STARS and x10 profit. (V3.0)
* @{"Statistics" link stats}
* @{"HighScore List" link hiscore}
* @{"Virtual Cards" link virtcard} By time cards get worn & dirty.
* Sfx (V1.5)
* A Lot Of Love!

@endnode

