ACESHIGH - Reactivates ACES HIGH (not STAR GAME)

Ex. Bet $10 with ACES HIGH and get 'Three of a kind'. $10 x 4 x 3 = $120
    Then Double it Three Times: $120 x 2 x 2 x 2 = $960 (Easy, eh?)

